<sect3 id="sect_definingEnumFields" label="5">
    <title id="title_definingEnumFields">Defining enum fields</title>
    <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup rowsep="0" cols="2" align="left" colsep="0">
            <colspec colwidth="1*"/>
            <colspec colwidth="3*"/>
            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry rowsep="1"/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Purpose</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>Table fields of the type <guimenuitem>ENUM</guimenuitem> are used to
                            limit the number of permitted values to a predefined set of values, e.g.
                            a set of colors, person types, article types etc..</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Type specific field details</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>
                            <figure id="fig_enumFieldDetails">
                                <title> Enum field details</title>
                                <screenshot>
                                    <mediaobject>
                                        <imageobject>
                                            <imagedata fileref="./Screenshots/EnumFieldDetails.jpg"
                                                format="JPEG" scalefit="1" width="237" depth="110"/>
                                        </imageobject>
                                    </mediaobject>
                                </screenshot>
                            </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>For enum fields you can specify the following field details:</para>
                        <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>a default value for the enum field by
                                    selecting a value from the <guilabel>Default</guilabel> combo
                                    box and</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>all permitted values have to be entered into the multiline
                                    text field <guilabel>Enum values</guilabel> separated from each
                                    other by carriage return-line feed.</para>
                            </listitem>
                        </itemizedlist>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry/>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
</sect3>
